<p>I wanted to reproduce a small Hello World Gtk program in Genie language, based in the following Vala code:</p>  <pre><code>using Gtk;  int main(string[] args){ Gtk.init (ref args); Gtk.Window window = new Gtk.Window (Gtk.WindowType.TOPLEVEL); Gtk.Label label = new Gtk.Label("Hello world!"); window.add(label);     window.set_default_size (300, 200);     window.show_all (); Gtk.main (); return 0; } </code></pre>  <p>How would the same code look in Genie?</p>